</span><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:
&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;color:#5A5A5A;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:165">🧠📘</span><span style="color:#5A5A5A;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:165">
